    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Start用圆形。Fetch阶段请把完整操作写清楚：PC送到MAR，内存内容读到MBR，再送到IR，最后PC自增。学生需要看到这些细节。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Start",
        "Fetch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Start和Fetch已经画好了，Fetch用矩形框，里面写上\"Fetch: PC → MAR, Mem[MAR] → MBR, MBR → IR, PC = PC + 1\"。接下来是Decode节点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Start",
        "Fetch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Decode阶段是控制单元译码IR，提取OPCODE和寻址模式，生成控制信号。然后Execute阶段要区分几种情况：ALU运算、LOAD/STORE访存、JMP/CALL改PC、CMP更新标志位。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Decode",
        "Execute"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Decode和Execute都加上了。Decode写\"UC decodifica IR, extrae OPCODE y MODE, genera señales de control\"，Execute把ALU、LOAD/STORE、JMP/CALL、CMP这几种情况都列进去了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Decode",
        "Execute"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来是Writeback，把结果写回寄存器或内存。然后需要一个判断节点检查是否是HLT指令，是的话就结束，否则循环回Fetch。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Writeback",
        "CheckHLT",
        "End"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
