      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "CheckHLT用菱形判断框，文字写\"¿Instrucción = HLT?\"，两条分支分别标\"Sí\"到End，\"No\"回到Fetch。End节点也用圆形，文字是\"Fin\"。这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CheckHLT",
        "End"
